IN 2005, LOCAL-CURRENCY

SALES GROWTH WAS BROAD BASED, WITH SELLING PRICES INCREASING 0.6%.  ALONG WITH THE BENEFITS PROVIDED BY 3MS

SOURCING INITIATIVE, 3MS PRICING STRATEGY HAS BEEN KEY TO MAINTAINING MARGINS

IN THE FACE OF SIGNIFICANT RAW MATERIAL PRICE PRESSURE.  3MS PRICING STRATEGY RESULTED IN U.S. PRICE

GROWTH OF 2.5% IN 2005.

